e":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T14:14:15.000Z","msg":"上連登，勿認真"},{"pid":"3311830c1d16836e45ed899a6ab0889cb4686e7e","tid":1121693,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T14:19:57.000Z","msg":"律師; 可以做 IPO / 普通solicitor  （其實都重有分好多鍾）"},{"pid":"e0f43c20a99b4e0730112313f92f600bc63022c0","tid":1121693,"uid":245813,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T14:20:00.000Z","msg":"咩返工，根本所有野都係咁<br />\n揀電話、揀戲睇、揀女朋友、揀移民地方、揀野食、揀衣著打扮、揀髮型...<br />\n有咩唔係唱到所有available嘅選擇都狗也不屌？<br />\n<br />\n到某樣野俾時代淘汰咗，成為咗歷史<br />\n連登仔就會吹返轉頭㗎喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7814eaa60ad930687945f8c252afa2d9af0b0c0","tid":1121693,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T14:20:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>律師; 可以做 IPO / 普通solicitor  （其實都重有分好多<span style=\"color: red;\">種</span>）</blockquote>"},{"pid":"e92a71769640c56a5d3b96e849179cd2d2c39c39","tid":1121693,"uid":239565,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T14:25:06.000Z","msg":"同我諗法一模一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n畢左業即刻apply政府工"},{"pid":"97e15a32b823655ccd3d268f1508dadcc6ef1602","tid":1121693,"uid":35315,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T17:43:32.000Z","msg":"依度梗係多人唱淡啦、唔唱啖咪更多對手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6dcb56c7c380855105d7c2b2292bbdbb815a676","tid":1121693,"uid":25003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a550a8a03fa25ffe2faaf95e69db0b1657eb240c","tid":1121693,"uid":71237,"like":49,"dislike":3,"score":46,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T13:14:41.000Z","msg":"連登仔啲心態好似玩手機game咁<br />\n抽唔到全game最勁嘅SSR就情願唔開局"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T17:50:31.000Z","msg":"玩手機game刷左5年半今日先開局<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54d815843379f960c4a6b0d9c80340058affd5f7","tid":1121693,"uid":75196,"like":3,"dis